      <section id="id1172542371721">
        <title>[LO 3.4]</title>
        <list id="id1172543612449" list-type="bulleted">
          <item>Once war and conflict ends, a country must rescue what is left!</item>
        </list>
        <para id="id1172542776054">a) Using the above information, take your time to think on these matters. Add <emphasis effect="bold">your personal insights </emphasis>and <emphasis effect="bold">describe the population </emphasis>of a country at the end of a twenty year period of armed conflict.</para>
        <para id="id1172543756712">b) If you were the secretary general of the United Nations, what would you do to prevent this type of war (and its consequences) in Africa?</para>
        <para id="id8711969">c) You are the <emphasis effect="bold">minister of population development and education </emphasis>of a country when a twenty year period of war has come to an end. What steps would you take to counter the damaging effects of war on the population to the best of your ability?</para>
